            "text": "https://api.ben2.ai/v1/infer",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", and set up authentication headers using your API key. Use environment variables to manage secrets securely, and implement retry logic with exponential backoff for initial connection tests. Ensure your client libraries are updated to handle HTTP/2 for improved multiplexing."
